	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The reason mappers are fast is that they are built from basic logic gates, like latches. They have no clock so they run as fast as the logic itself runs.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
